Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
timing_ignore...on_data_checks(25.10)    timing_ignore...on_data_checks(25.10)

Name
       timing_ignore_clock_based_path_delay_on_data_checks

Syntax
       timing_ignore_clock_based_path_delay_on_data_checks

       {true | false}

       Default: false

       Disables clock-based path delay application on data checks.

       When set to true, the Tempus software enables the data checks to be re-
       ported  by disabling the applied path delay. The "Data Check Setup" de-
       tails are displayed in the timing report output.

       When set to false, the timing reports display the "Path Delay" details.
       By default, this global variable is set to false.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

